 &ndash; U.S. Senators Marco Rubio (R-FL), Tom Cotton (R-AR), Chuck Schumer (D-NY), and Chris Van Hollen (D-MD) today released the following statement on the passage of a bipartisan ZTE amendment in the John S. McCain National Defense Authorization Act for Fiscal Year 2019:<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;We&rsquo;re heartened that both parties made it clear that protecting American jobs and national security must come first when making deals with countries like China, which has a history of having little regard for either. It is vital that our colleagues in the House keep this bipartisan provision in the bill as it heads towards a conference.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rubio.senate.gov/public/index.cfm?p=Press-Releases&amp;id=8221665B-221F-4845-AFE1-34B94F75BE66\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rubio.senate.gov%2Fpublic%2Findex.cfm%3Fp%3DPress-Releases%26id%3D8221665B-221F-4845-AFE1-34B94F75BE66&d=vqM4mCGDxYbl5X62wekB3nIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=22f551e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rubio.senate.gov/public/index.cfm?p=Press-Releases&amp;id=8221665B-221F-4845-AFE1-34B94F75BE66</a>"},{"pid":"9e5257d6c214f69eb0ff9a3b2b3adc11dda2c4ec","tid":707771,"uid":34705,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T04:40:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>參議院議員早前表明不願給予中興第二次機會。<span style=\"color: red;\">共和黨阿肯色州參議員柯頓直言，儘管最後達成的中興懲罰已相當重，但認為死刑較為合適。</span></blockquote><br />\n呢句OK 喎！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b84c644f48253db9b87e51e050e094e688b8bc52","tid":707771,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T04:47:34.000Z","msg":"叫住啲人唔好撈，要死果然係阻止唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f375729f28db4ed1136f840e2a336f78d954ca1c","tid":707771,"uid":15205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b84c644f48253db9b87e51e050e094e688b8bc52","